description: Proposed demolition of existing office building and erection of two buildings of between eight and ten storeys accommodating 248 dwellings (84 x 1-bedroom, 108 x 2-bedroom, 49 x 3-bedroom & 7 x 4-bedroom units) and flexible commercial space at ground floor (for Use Classes A1, A2, A3, A4 and/or B1(a)), new public square, landscaped communal gardens, associated landscape works, alterations to existing crossover(s) and basement car and cycle parking  and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 15 September 2016 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended
